2. **obeticholic acid Ocaliva 2016 → withdrawn 2023 NASH** = first FDA PBC + REGENERATE Phase 3 NASH endpoint hit but FDA reject 2020 + 2023 hepatic decompensation withdrawn. FXR agonist class lessons — pruritus + LDL elevation + hepatic decompensation 부작용. quantum-VQE 의 FXR LBD selectivity + tropifexor + vonafexor next-gen 비교 한정.
3. **GLP-1/dual/triple agonist 2024** = semaglutide ESSENCE Phase 3 + tirzepatide SYNERGY-NASH Phase 3 + survodutide GLP-1+glucagon + retatrutide GIP+GLP-1+glucagon. obesity primary axis + MASH secondary endpoint 동시 달성 임상 패러다임 — "weight loss + MASH 동시" multi-target. quantum-VQE 의 peptide-receptor multi-binding modeling 한정.
4. **FGF21 + FGF19 mimetic 2024** = efruxifermin + pegozafermin FGF21 Phase 3 + aldafermin FGF19 Phase 3. metabolic + 만성 fibrosis 동시 개선 paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 FGFR-βKlotho complex modeling 한정.
5. **SCD1 + FASN + ACC + ASK1 + CCR2/CCR5 failures 2019-2024** = aramchol + denifanstat + firsocostat + selonsertib + cenicriviroc Phase 3 fail. de novo lipogenesis + inflammation + fibrosis target class 임상 한계. quantum-VQE 의 lessons-learned + next-gen redesign 기회.
6. **MASLD/MASH 2023 renaming (NAFLD → MASLD, NASH → MASH)** = AASLD + EASL + ALEH multi-society consensus → metabolic etiology 강조 + ALD overlap MetALD subcategory. 임상 trial endpoint + ICD code + biomarker 재정렬.
7. **pan-PPAR α/δ/γ lanifibranor NATIV3** = Phase 3 진행 — pioglitazone (γ alone) + elafibranor (α/δ) 한계 후 pan-PPAR 가 broader metabolic + 만성 fibrosis 동시 개선 가능성.
8. **PNPLA3 I148M + TM6SF2 + HSD17B13 genetic variants** = MASH/NAFLD 만성 hereditary risk + AZD2693 (PNPLA3 ASO) + JNJ-75220795 (HSD17B13 ASO) Phase 1-2 진행. allele-selective RIBOZYME 직접 fit.
